        <div class="col-md-12" id="xtalk" style="padding-top:100px">
            <h3>Secure Mobile Communication App - XTalk</h3>
            <p style="text-align:justify">
                X-Talk is a secured mobile communication app specially designed for the corporate world. With sensitive data being shared through the net these days, X-Talk provides end-end encryption and personalized message controls to mitigate the risk of data theft.
                It can also be easily hosted on any server.  
                <br />
                In comparison with other social apps, this app has unique secure features:
                <ul>
                    <li>Bio-metric Authentication.</li>
                    <li>Message controls (time and transfer based controls).</li>
                    <li>Admin panel access.</li>
                    <li>Customization as per customer's requirements.</li>
                </ul> 

            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-12" id="wd" style="padding-top:100px">
            <h3>Website Development</h3>
            <p style="text-align:justify">
                   Website bridges the gap between your business objective and your target audience. The web today, has become no more content specific but open and flexible, both via mobile and desktop browsers.
                   Over the last five years, the tools available to developers have matured and allows for a faster development, reduction in maintainance costs, increase in flexibility and an advanced user experience.
                   Our development team has experience in .NET Core, ASP.NET, Angular JS and HTML5.
                <br />
                Features:
                <ul>
                    <li>Responsive Web Development</li>
                    <li>Service Worker</li>
                    <li>Progressive Web Applications</li>
                    <li>HTML5</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
        </div>
